{"tid":2196173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"秋風蕭瑟天氣涼","createTime":"2020-09-09T16:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T16:48:30.000Z","uid":343520,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d68bd60179e2314b818f114a0d3387a66a07664","tid":2196173,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"秋風蕭瑟天氣涼，草木搖落露爲霜，羣燕辭歸鵠南翔。<br />\n<br />\n念君客遊思斷腸，慊慊思歸戀故鄉，君何淹留寄他方？<br />\n<br />\n賤妾煢煢守空房，憂來思君不敢忘，不覺淚下沾衣裳。<br />\n<br />\n援琴鳴弦發清商，短歌微吟不能長。<br />\n<br />\n明月皎皎照我牀，星漢西流夜未央。<br />\n<br />\n牽牛織女遙相望，爾獨何辜限河梁。"},{"pid":"f8849514856b695aa0f506b04625955d5ea6d08a","tid":2196173,"uid":186708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"&radic;&radic;"},{"pid":"0770073a15a99135ceb1bcb898cbcb1f3d88a684","tid":2196173,"uid":367456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}